  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Pharmacodynamic Effects of SAGE-217 in Healthy Adults Using an Insomnia Model</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Multiple Dose, 3-way Crossover, Exploratory Study to Assess the Pharmacodynamic Effects of SAGE-217 Capsules in Healthy Adults Using a 5-hour Phase Advance Model of Insomnia</official_title>
